Alpha:

vector_neut(-ts_corr(returns,scl12_sentiment,50),close)

Hypothesis:

Stocks that exhibit a strong negative correlation between returns and sentiment over a 50-day period, when neutralized by their 
closing prices, present trading opportunities that can be exploited to generate alpha.

Research Paper: https://support.worldquantbrain.com/hc/en-us/community/posts/13954113156503-Research-Paper-01-The-Momentum-of-News
